                    <div id="divInfo" class="divAll">                        
                        <p class="compInfo">For a very long time now Pets-R-Us has been serving our dear customers. 
                            We have been selling variety of pet-related products, supplies, services, and accessories. 
                            We also have been offering variety of pets for adoption.
                             We are the top pet store in every community that we have a location in. 
                            Recently we decided to increase the list of services what we provide. 
                            This list includes dog grooming, training, and boarding. 
                            As result of our new services, we created this website. You can now book any of the services that we mentioned on this site.                     
                        </p>
                        <p class="compInfo">Pets-R-Us was founded in 2007 by married couple Manuel and Rachel. 
                            They started Pet-R-Us because they love pets. All together they had a total of 25 various pets at their house. 
                            The idea to start the shop came when Manuel was driving around and noticed someone dropped some puppies at the side of the road and drove off. 
                            Manuel realized that there are a lot of pets that don’t have a home, so he and wife decided to start Pets-R-US. 
                            The store started off providing pet adaption services. Then selling some pet-related products.
                        </p>
                        <p class="compInfo">The company is growing tremendously. 
                            When they first started the company, they were the only employees. 
