                            They were the first two workers. 
                            They ran all the business activities from there. After five months in the basement, Manuel and Maury had to relocate to a bigger location.                   
                        </p>
                        <p class="compInfo compInfo2">The first official location that Pet-R-US had is found at 13530 Discovery Dr Suite 15, Omaha, NE 68137. 
